### Banner API Test (Admin)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4001/api/v1

### 0. Login as Admin
# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### 1. [Admin] Get all banners (including inactive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners

### 2. [Admin] Create new banner (Home Hero)
# @name createBanner
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

New Year Sale 2024
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="linkUrl"

/category/Notebook
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="placement"

home_hero
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="order"

1
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="isActive"

true
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="hero.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ../../test-images/product-sample-1.png
--boundary--

### 3. [Admin] Update banner (Partial - Change title only)
# แก้ไขเฉพาะชื่อ โดยไม่ส่งรูปภาพ (รูปเดิมต้องยังอยู่)
@bannerId = {{createBanner.response.body.data._id}}
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners/{{bannerId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Extended Summer Sale"
}

### 4. [Admin] Delete banner
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners/{{bannerId}}

### 5. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/logout
